dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially.  Mainly shows coast of South Carolina.  In lower margin: Reproduced for the Hon. William A. Courtenay, LL. D., of South Carolina, from the original map in the Public Records Office, London.  Originally from Du Val, P. Diverses cartes et tables. Paris, [1669?].
dcat_keyword_sm: South Carolina Maps Early Works to 1800
